{"tid":2033720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「香港人走得快D走，唔使講其他野！」","createTime":"2020-05-24T23:04:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T22:05:19.000Z","uid":202464,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"89b32116a025978ff938e2f4e02d8d47c792a623","tid":2033720,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T23:04:27.000Z","msg":"1.  一位出身支那新聞界現居美國的朋友，22日在微信上說：「香港朋友能跑趕緊跑，沒甚麼好說的。」那是對港版國安法即時反應。<br />\n<br />\n2.  英國歷史學家Eric Hobsbawm引用過一句意大利農婦的話，「快逃，祖國來了！」<br />\n<br />\n這句話的「祖國」，不是指自己列祖列宗生活的土地、文化和人民，而是指一個實行國家主義的政權。<br />\n<br />\n3. 過去香港人未感到要「趕緊跑」，因為「祖國」認為時機還未成熟。港版國安法就赤裸裸傳出要我們「趕緊跑」的訊息了。<br />\n<br />\n4. 「趕緊跑」的不止是人，還有錢。在支那：「你存在支那的錢不是真正屬於你的，只有移往國外才是屬於你的；你的親屬也不是真正屬於你的，只有把他們移往國外，才真正屬於你的。」<br />\n<br />\n5. 支那不論哪個階層，都越來越多人染上這種「棄國病」。上周五香港股市和港元匯率已經作出了「棄港」的市場反應。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b80da9bdd94d66145f157ef68af733f1ad83b05b","tid":2033720,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T23:11:05.000Z","msg":"認同請分享。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"167a152873575fca024b77dfce0b3d5f7c823f66","tid":2033720,"uid":202464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T23:15:24.000Z","msg":"好人一生平安。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60285c29ff1379e0be33bc1999bdfc60531baa02","tid":2033720,"uid":202464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T23:30:10.000Z","msg":"連登子：「樓主傳播失敗主義！拉！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a021e8338fcff5189905855cafa90f0a4867c5e","tid":2033720,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T00:15:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7ac7be49f920c343f7281acaacadc2c9ab1ac5e","tid":2033720,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:14:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e8367df8e144e48bce29a743eb1617f5534ec57","tid":2033720,"uid":122709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:25:44.000Z","msg":"不如copy哂李怡篇文啦，唔好斷章取義"},{"pid":"43cdd3b49db9bb9a6abc81e7a957ceb0b809d24c","tid":2033720,"uid":202464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4e8367df8e144e48bce29a743eb1617f5534ec57","tid":2033720,"uid":122709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:25:44.000Z","msg":"不如copy哂李怡篇文啦，唔好斷章取義"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T09:40:34.000Z","msg":"copy重點已經夠<br />\n<br />\n<br />\ncopy太多連登仔tldr"},{"pid":"e5523dbcdfd856624b99075babe0ca904d4c6b38","tid":2033720,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T09:42:04.000Z","msg":"又係白宮聯署: 港版國安法一成立, 取消香港關係法, 獨立關稅區, 敏感科技不准入香港<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-abolishment-us-hk-policy-act-once-hk-security-law-established\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequest-abolishment-us-hk-policy-act-once-hk-security-law-established&d=1ElP8QZN%2FBtuydBCWvxAMo6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=084a1950\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-abolishment-us-hk-policy-act-once-hk-security-law-established</a>"},{"pid":"870c1b4f6969be0aa3e6a3e0e4feaeccc56581dc","tid":2033720,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5523dbcdfd856624b99075babe0ca904d4c6b38","tid":2033720,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"